---

<section>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl lg:px-16 md:px-12 px-8 xl:px-24 py-24">
    <span class="text-sm uppercase font-medium tracking-wide text-blue-600"
      >pricing</span
    >
    <h2
      class="text-purple-900 font-semibold tracking-tight lg:text-5xl mt-6 text-3xl lg:text-balance">
      Always know what you'll pay, transparent pricing for everyone.
    </h2>
    <p class="text-slate-500 mt-5 lg:text-balance ">
      Choose a plan that works the best for you and your team. Start small,
      upgrade when you need.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12 space-y-4">
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-5 border rounded-xl overflow-clip">
        <div class="flex flex-col flex-shrink-0 mb-6 md:mb-0 lg:col-span-2 p-4">
          <span class="font-semibold text-purple-900 text-xl"
            >Recruiting Services
          </span>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:col-span-3">
          <div
            class="lg:col-span-2 p-4 border-t border-l-0 lg:border-l lg:border-t-0">
            <p class="font-semibold text-purple-900">
              Sourcing as a Service
            </p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-slate-500 text-sm">
              Obtain bank names and tokenized account numbers to connect a
              user’s bank account and verify that it’s open.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-50 border-l-2 border-blue-500">
            <div class="p-4 border-t lg:border-t-0">
              <p class="font-semibold text-purple-900">Pricing</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-slate-500 text-sm">Depends on the amount of roles per month</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-3 lg:col-start-3">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3">
            <div class="lg:col-span-2 p-4 border-t lg:border-l border-l-0">
              <p class="font-semibold text-purple-900">Account owners</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-slate-500 text-sm">
                Pull account owner information, such as first name, last name,
                and address.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-slate-50 border-l-2 border-blue-500">
              <div class="p-4 border-t">
                <p class="font-semibold text-purple-900">Pricing</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-slate-500 text-sm">
                  Roughly 25% of the first year's base salary depending on the role
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-5 pt-6 border-t">
        <div class="flex flex-col flex-shrink-0 mb-6 md:mb-0 lg:col-span-2">
          <span class="font-semibold text-purple-900 text-xl"
            >Custom Plans
          </span>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-3">
          <div class="lg:col-span-2">
            <p class="mt-2 text-slate-500 text-sm">
              If you need more job posts or recruiting services, let's find a time to see how we can help
              you hire your next great employee. 
            </p>
            <p>
              <a
                title="link to your page"
                aria-label="your label"
                href="mailto:will@tustinrecruiting.com"
                class="text-blue-600 font-semibold hover:text-purple-900 text-sm inline-flex items-center group">
                Contact sales
              </a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
